There is a little source about using NameFromLock...

Function$ fullpath {f$}
; Convert relative path to FULL path
; examples:   IN: SYS:t/1 -> OUT: Workbench:t/1
; CD SYS:t... IN: 1       -> OUT: Workbench:t/1

  puff$=SPACE$(1024)                  ; create puffer
  lock.l=Lock_(&f$,-2)                ; lock for reading
  a=NameFromLock_(lock,&puff$,#maxln) ; name from lock
  UnLock_(lock)                       ; unlock
  b$=Peek$(&puff$)                    ; reading from puffer
  Function Return b$
End Function

